 valign="middle" >整改方法及措施的合理性</td></tr></tbody></table></table-wrap><p>表1. 体育硕士学位论文质量监控体系</p><table-wrap id="table2" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table2">Table 2</xref></label><caption><title> Quality monitoring system index weight of master degree thesis of P</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle" >一级指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >权重</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >二级指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >权重</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >三级指标</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >权重</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="8"  >B1</td><td align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="8"  >0.785</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C11</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0373</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C12</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.2366</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C13</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0582</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C14</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.1852</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C15</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.2452</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C16</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.0217</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" ></td><td align="center" valign="middle" >C17</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.1783</td></tr><tr><td align="center"